memoryItems.memory: One day sausage doggy ate a whole cake and slept for 24 hours. He was so happy.
Rosemary loved animals and used to spend all her time with them. She loved her dog Spot in particular, and we went on many walks together.
Lara was a brilliant, funny person. She had the best laugh and I remember spending hours together laughing about anything and everything.
Jake loved his pet lizard so much, they were the best of buddies. They went on many adventures together and were both super big-hearted and chill.
Lindsay was so creative and fun. She was a costume designer and taught me how to sew.
Graham was the life of the party and always brought people together. I loved how adventurous he was.
Mark was quiet and musical and a kind person. We spent many evenings playing guitar together.
Leah was a brilliant soul and a fantastic musician. My proudest moments were watching her perform.
Molly was a joyful, warm person. We loved doing pottery together and met in a pottery class.
Dan was such a kind, smart person. He was always up to play a joke on people and was loyal to a fault.

memoryItems.itemName: Johnny The Great's memory of Melissa
memoryItems.memory: Melissa was a goofy, sweet person and I loved her laugh. She always had time for a chat and we had many good times.
Alice was a fun loving person. She was so creative and loved to make us all laugh.
